videos.description: Boston College's Ky Bowman rises for a tomahawk slam, but is stood up by Jack White on the block.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Duke's White reverse-posterizes Bowman on dunk denial) 2019/2/5

videos.headline: Duke's White reverse-posterizes Bowman on dunk denial

videos.description: Ky Bowman rebounds a Cam Reddish missed 3, pushes the pace and hits Steffon Mitchell for the wild backward lay-in.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Mitchell gets spinning, circus layup to fall for BC) 2019/2/5

videos.headline: Mitchell gets spinning, circus layup to fall for BC

videos.description: Cam Reddish is off the mark on a triple before halftime, but picks the pocket of Ky Bowman and lays it in at the horn.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Reddish regathers miss, beats buzzer with finger-roll finish) 2019/2/5

videos.headline: Reddish regathers miss, beats buzzer with finger-roll finish

videos.description: Zion Williamson finishes the first half just a point shy of a double-double with nine points and 10 boards, as Duke trails Boston College by 2.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Zion nearly etches double-double at half) 2019/2/5 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Zion nearly etches double-double at half

videos.description: RJ Barrett receives a handoff from Tre Jones and steamrolls to the cup past Ky Bowman for the lefty finish plus the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Barrett burns by Bowman for and-1 layup) 2019/2/5

videos.headline: Barrett burns by Bowman for and-1 layup

videos.description: Ky Bowman answers Cam Reddish's third triple of the game with a lightning end-to-end score on the tomahawk flush.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bowman bolts to rim, bashes dunk after Reddish 3) 2019/2/5

videos.headline: Bowman bolts to rim, bashes dunk after Reddish 3

videos.description: Zion Williamson has an open floor all to himself, but misses the ridiculous reverse jam.
videos.headline: Zion blows breakway dunk

videos.description: Cam Reddish is double teamed on the baseline and hits a cutting Zion Williamson, who loses it on his way up, appearing frustrated on the bench.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Zion botches 2nd open-dunk attempt of game) 2019/2/5

videos.headline: Zion botches 2nd open-dunk attempt of game

videos.description: Allison Williams speaks with Cam Reddish following his 24-point performance, saying he looks up to Paul George, but simply wants to create his own identity at the next level.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Interview (Reddish on NBA comparison: 'I just wanna be myself') 2019/2/5

videos.headline: Reddish on NBA comparison: 'I just wanna be myself'

videos.description: Zion Williamson uncharacteristically misses multiple open dunk attempts, but still finishes with 16 points and 17 rebounds in Duke's win vs. BC.
